snippet.title: BIKE RAMPAGE!
snippet.description:
Download Bike Rampage by KennyCatches: https://sites.google.com/view/thundagas-games/pog-jam-3

Thundaga plays through games made for the Pog Jam 3!
Pog Jam 3 Site: https://sites.google.com/view/thundagas-games/pog-jam-3 
Pog Jam Discord: https://discord.com/invite/gxBscxYzud

The Pog Jam is a weeklong game jam where we all make fun, short, and goofy games! PJ2 was a massive success with 20 entries, so it only made since to come back with a PJ3 and try to make things bigger and better!

#thundaga #pogjam3
